{{Unlicensed}}'''Gordunga''' was a being who hired two thugs, one of whom was [[Falcon (person)|Falcon]], to retrieve the [[Nova Crystal]] from [[Pothos Fine]] and to murder him. He had arranged to meet Falcon in the [[Wandering Bantha Casino]] after the job was completed.

